  "text": "In [CITATION_1] , the author proposed a novel encoding framework to transform time series to images as the input for deep convolution neural networks and achieve the state-of-theart classification performance. We found proposed temporal Markov encoding maps have exact/approximate inverse maps, making such transformation more interpretable with graph visualization techniques.",
